    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    Increase AC adding shielding spell by blurring the target's image which therefore is more difficult to see and thus hit. Caster's level determines AC increase.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>General<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Adds to AC
